
1. Setup a Catalog Item (POST /api/rewards)
JSON
// POST http://localhost:8080/api/rewards
{
  "id": "reward-screentime",
  "title": "1 Hour Screen Time",
  "description": "Unlock video games or streaming on the living room TV.",
  "costPoints": 100,
  "stock": 5
}
Expected Response (201 Created): Returns the saved reward layout object.


2. Execute a Purchase (POST with Query Action)
Let’s simulate a performer user checking out this item from the catalog storefront.

Plaintext
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rewards?action=purchase&id=reward-screentime&userId=child-timmy

Scenario A (Timmy doesn't have 100 points):
JSON
{"error": "Transaction Denied: Insufficient ledger balance. Need 100 points, but only have 40."}

Scenario B (Timmy has enough points):
JSON
{
  "message": "Purchase successful! Deducted 100 credits from Timmy Smith.",
  "remainingBalance": 100
}

If you re-run a GET http://localhost:8080/api/rewards, the catalog state on disk will accurately reflect that stock dropped from 5 to 4.


3. Example A: Creating an Individual Reward (POST /api/rewards)
An individual reward assigned exclusively to child-timmy:
JSON
{
  "id": "reward-timmy-bike",
  "title": "New Bicycle",
  "description": "Red mountain bike.",
  "costPoints": 500,
  "stock": 1,
  "type": "INDIVIDUAL",
  "targetProfileId": "child-timmy"
}

4. Example B: Creating a Group Reward (POST /api/rewards)
A shared group reward assigned to the entire kids' group (e.g., a family trip to a theme park):
JSON
{
  "id": "reward-disney-trip",
  "title": "Family Waterpark Pass",
  "description": "Day pass to the waterpark for the whole family.",
  "costPoints": 1000,
  "stock": 1,
  "type": "GROUP",
  "targetGroupId": "group-all-kids"
}

5. Performers Contribute Points (POST /api/rewards)
Timmy contributes 300 points to the Waterpark Pass:
Plaintext
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rewards?action=contribute&id=reward-waterpark&userId=child-timmy&amount=300
Response:
JSON
{
  "message": "Contribution saved. Progress: 300/1000",
  "userRemainingBalance": 50
}

6. Final Contribution Unlocks Reward
Sarah contributes the remaining 700 points:
Plaintext
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rewards?action=contribute&id=reward-waterpark&userId=child-sarah&amount=700
Response:
JSON
{
  "message": "🎉 Goal Reached! Group Reward UNLOCKED for everyone!",
  "userRemainingBalance": 100
}